Letter from Kim Schools
Good Morning Mr. Stagner,
I wanted to write to you today to tell you how much I was impressed by your athletes, coaches, students and parents on their trip to Kim School on Saturday. Everyone I talked to was courteous, pleasant, respectful of others and themselves, and a joy to host. I have been involved with high school athletics for over 20 years and it isn’t often I feel compelled to extort the positive behavior of an opponent. Your contingent of community members did your school proud and I feel you should know we would be honored to meet with you again on the playing field or basketball court.
Have a great day.
Sincerely,
Blake Byall—Kim School Superintendent










